  ],
  "remarks": "JSC Vistan is a Belarusian manufacturer of machine tools, including CNC machining centres, cylindrical grinders, centreless grinding machines, gear processing equipment, and lathes. These are dual-use technologies used in the production of military goods. JSC Vistan exports over 60 % of its products to Russia and supplies machine tools to Russian defence-related enterprises, including JSC “Krasny Oktyabr”. The company is part of a Belarus-Russia import-substitution program and is receiving US$15 000 000 in funding backed by Russian state financial support, to expand gear-processing machine production.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}